{
  "stem": "7739.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They brought out some other boys from there, joined our group, and they marched us to a place called Hof Birkenau, which was a farm.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was all part of the Auschwitz complex.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were only one barracks of prisoners there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There were a barracks outside of a few guards, and of course, there were the overseers, the Kapos.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we worked on a farm there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We figured, by God, we're going to be work on a farm.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It's going to be wonderful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "All they had on the farm is horses and cows.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they had-- the crop were there was sugar beets.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we tried to eat the sugar beets.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So a few guys got caught eating the sugar beets.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was cold winter already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "If you were cold-- if you were caught eating the sugar beets, they would take you outside, stuck a sugar beet in your mouth, kick it in, kick all your teeth out, and leave you there on your knees in the wintertime.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And you were bleeding like a pig.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So you learned not to steal sugar beets anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But there was oats, and I used to come steal sometimes a handful of oats and eat it from the horses.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Once I was caught, and luckily, this Kapo was an old German.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He-- he seemed so ancient, and I've never seen an old person like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Criminal prisoner, bastard, going around all day cursing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He caught me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he said he's going to give me a caning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So I was ready.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He says, go get yourself a cane.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So I looked around in the barn there, and I made sure I got a heavy one so you don't feel the whips so much as you feel by a-- a-- a-- a thinner one.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
